Text:
So what's in this torrent?
"Crap I found on the corner" hardly sells it.
1.41 Gb in one file BEFORE we know.

Try elaborating.

Curiosity really got us with this one. Give people a vague description and we jump on it, wanting to know what it is. Please don't waste your time downloading this. I'm actually surprised the uploader continued to seed this. Photos of a couple with their kids and friends. A few Vids thrown in, some with their children and some of drunken parties.
